      *-----------------------------------------------------
      *  MAIN ROUTINE
      *-----------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P1FIXD  80
     C                     PARM           P1FIXT  60
     C                     PARM           P9EXTR  30
      *
     C                     TIME           WTIME
      *
     C           KEYCA     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           P1FIXD
     C                     KFLD           P1FIXT
